We are switching over to JIRA for our support tickets and we would like the option to be able to use a 0-10 because "1-5 scales doesn't yield sufficient diversity in the data to enable key optimal driver analysis".  Also 0-10 is the scale we currently use for NPS and all of our reports and historical data are on that scale.

 

I realize that currently CSAT offers a 1-5 scale, but we need 0-10 and we would also like to be able to customize the text for each rating (which has been requested by other people in JSD-3436 and JSD-4002).

