h3. Problem Definition 

At [Enabling public signup and CAPTCHA|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/AdminJIRAServer073/Enabling+public+signup+and+CAPTCHA] and [here|https://confluence.atlassian.com/adminjiraserver072/enabling-public-signup-and-captcha-828787685.html] under section *Enabling public signup for JIRA Service Desk*
